238
00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:30,130
<i>(Hiroki)</i>
<i>Definitely. You can accomplish</i>
<i>so much more than when you're</i>
<i>all by yourself.</i>

239
00:14:30,163 --> 00:14:34,367
<i>If you trust other people, put</i>
<i>your faith in them, there's no</i>
<i>telling what you can't</i>
<i>accomplish</i>

240
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:37,904
