244
00:14:47,648 --> 00:14:52,986
No, I think I'm all right now.

245
00:14:53,019 --> 00:14:54,487
Okay.

246
00:14:54,521 --> 00:14:57,423
Alright, then, so are you
ready to watch me fly?

247
00:14:57,423 --> 00:15:00,266
<i>(Ves‐Ves)</i>
<i>Mankind has always yearned</i>
<i>for the skies.</i>

248
00:15:00,266 --> 00:15:01,602
Huh?

249
00:15:01,602 --> 00:15:04,004
