contraption like that in order
to fly.

251
00:15:07,273 --> 00:15:08,742
I can fly wherever I want!

252
00:15:08,775 --> 00:15:10,611
I don't need some
stupid machine...

253
00:15:10,677 --> 00:15:12,412
That's so cool...

254
00:15:12,445 --> 00:15:14,447
What do you want?
Who are you!?

255
00:15:14,447 --> 00:15:16,349
Hey, no need to be suspicious.

256
00:15:16,382 --> 00:15:18,619
I'm just a fellow lover
of the soaring skies.

257
00:15:18,685 --> 00:15:22,455
You seem very suspicious to me,
just by the way you're dressed!

258
00:15:22,455 --> 00:15:24,290
Really?

259
00:15:24,290 --> 00:15:27,928
This looks suspicious to you?

260
00:15:27,961 --> 00:15:29,530
‐Mhm!
‐Mhm!

261
00:15:29,563 --> 00:15:32,365
So, not like I'm the typical
girl next door?

262
00:15:32,398 --> 00:15:34,100
‐Nope. Not at all.
‐Nope. Not at all.

263
00:15:34,134 --> 00:15:38,539
“Ohmigosh! I totally wanna be
best friends with her! ” You
don't feel like that?

264
00:15:38,572 --> 00:15:40,040
‐Not in the slightest.
‐Not in the slightest.

265
00:15:40,073 --> 00:15:43,209
Well, thanks a lot for ruining
what I thought was a pretty good
disguise.

266
00:15:43,243 --> 00:15:44,978
Couple a' smarty‐pants!

267
00:15:44,978 --> 00:15:48,815
You're floating on a ball in
midair, how could you not seem
suspicious?

268
00:15:48,815 --> 00:15:49,650
Mm‐hm!

269
00:15:49,716 --> 00:15:51,652
<i>(Ves‐Ves)</i>
<i>Fine, who cares anyway?</i>

270
00:15:51,818 --> 00:15:53,820
[giggle]

271
00:15:55,488 --> 00:15:59,092
Now, let's have a look at that
Dream Mirror of yours, shall we?

272
00:16:02,002 --> 00:16:03,670
Orb Shot!

273
00:16:04,605 --> 00:16:05,839
[gasps]

274
00:16:05,906 --> 00:16:08,008
Watch out! Chibi‐Usa!

275
00:16:08,074 --> 00:16:09,576
[screaming]

276
00:16:09,610 --> 00:16:10,811
Oh no!

277
00:16:10,844 --> 00:16:14,347
Chibi‐Usa! You okay?!

278
00:16:14,414 --> 00:16:17,350
[grunt]

279
00:16:17,350 --> 00:16:18,852
Hiroki!

280
00:16:21,522 --> 00:16:22,322
[giggle]

281
00:16:22,355 --> 00:16:25,692
Hiroki!

282
00:16:27,093 --> 00:16:31,031
Oh no. Another dud? What
a total waste of a dibs.

283
00:16:31,097 --> 00:16:34,535
Ohh, man. Another bum lead from
Granny Zirconia...

284
00:16:34,535 --> 00:16:36,770
I swear, she must be
getting senile.

285
00:16:36,803 --> 00:16:40,607
And now I've got to stay here
and clean up this mess!

286
00:16:40,641 --> 00:16:42,108
<i>(Chibi Moon )</i>
<i>Hold it right there!</i>

287
00:16:42,142 --> 00:16:45,378
You would take away the wings
in a young boy's heart?

288
00:16:45,378 --> 00:16:49,716
I...won't ...let...you!

289
00:16:49,716 --> 00:16:52,953
Oh, so you're
by yourself today?

290
00:16:52,986 --> 00:16:56,122
I am the Pretty Guardian who
fights for love and for justice!

291
00:16:56,156 --> 00:16:57,891
I am Sailor Chibi Moon!

292
00:16:57,891 --> 00:17:00,561
Hel‐lo?! I asked if
you're by yourself today!

293
00:17:00,561 --> 00:17:04,638
And...in the name of the
Moon, I'll punish you!

294
00:17:04,671 --> 00:17:06,472
Can't you just answer
the question?!

295
00:17:06,507 --> 00:17:08,474
Are you by yourself or not?!

296
00:17:08,509 --> 00:17:12,145
I don't need anyone else's help
to take care of you!

297
00:17:12,178 --> 00:17:14,581
What, are you gonna
ring me to death?

298
00:17:14,581 --> 00:17:16,082
Ding dong!

299
00:17:16,149 --> 00:17:18,885
Ow! Ow ow ow ow!

300
00:17:18,919 --> 00:17:24,257
All right, you! Come forth my
Lemures, Pao‐Pao Girl, the
Dream‐Eating Mammoth!

301
00:17:24,257 --> 00:17:30,496
Pao!... I'm Pao‐Pao Girl, the
Dream‐Eating Mammoth!

302
00:17:30,531 --> 00:17:32,432
Pao‐Pao‐Pao‐Pao!

303
00:17:32,432 --> 00:17:35,669
[attack scream]

304
00:17:35,702 --> 00:17:37,203
[scream]

305
00:17:38,772 --> 00:17:41,107
(Ves‐Ves)
If you think that's bad, wait'll
you see what she does to <i>you!</i>

306
00:17:41,107 --> 00:17:42,576
[gasp]

307
00:17:42,609 --> 00:17:45,946
While you're at it, Pao‐Pao
Girl, devour that Dream Mirror,
will you?

308
00:17:45,946 --> 00:17:48,248
Pao‐Pao!

309
00:17:48,281 --> 00:17:49,449
No, don't‐‐!

310
00:17:49,449 --> 00:17:52,553
Paaooo Pao!

311
00:17:56,122 --> 00:17:57,290
[gasps]

312
00:17:58,291 --> 00:18:00,426
You guys!

313
00:18:00,460 --> 00:18:03,469
I hope you're not too stubborn
to accept some help.

314
00:18:03,469 --> 00:18:04,871
Where did they come from?

315
00:18:04,905 --> 00:18:07,207
Pao‐Pao Girl! Go on,
get rid of them!

316
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:08,642
Pao!

317
00:18:08,709 --> 00:18:15,048
Mars...Flame...Sniper!

318
00:18:16,416 --> 00:18:25,491
Mercury...Aqua Rhapsody!

319
00:18:25,491 --> 00:18:28,494
Paaoooo!

320
00:18:28,494 --> 00:18:30,396
Now's your chance, Chibi Moon!

321
00:18:30,430 --> 00:18:34,234
Right! Please, Pegasu‐‐ [gasp]

322
00:18:41,441 --> 00:18:42,909
(All)
Chibi Moon?

323
00:18:42,943 --> 00:18:44,978
...Sorry.

324
00:18:45,011 --> 00:18:46,346
Whatta you mean?

325
00:18:46,412 --> 00:18:47,681
What's the matter?

326
00:18:47,748 --> 00:18:50,350
Pegasus won't come
to me anymore...

327
00:18:50,350 --> 00:18:52,853
...I can't call him...

328
00:18:52,919 --> 00:18:56,022
I don't have the right
to call him ever again!

329
00:18:57,858 --> 00:19:01,502
I don't know what's going on,
but now's your chance! Get 'em!

330
00:19:01,535 --> 00:19:03,837
Paohhhhh! Paohhhhh! Paohhhhh!

331
00:19:03,870 --> 00:19:05,706
Chibi Moon!

332
00:19:05,772 --> 00:19:07,708
<i>(Sailor Moon)</i>
<i>Chibi Moon!... Watch out!</i>

333
00:19:07,708 --> 00:19:10,043
[grunts]

334
00:19:11,044 --> 00:19:14,047
Sailor Moon,
are you all right?

335
00:19:14,047 --> 00:19:16,049
I'm fine, don't worry...

336
00:19:16,049 --> 00:19:21,287
Chibi Moon, listen: I don't know
what happened, but you just have
to have more faith in yourself.

337
00:19:21,321 --> 00:19:23,189
Faith in myself?

338
00:19:23,223 --> 00:19:27,393
Mm‐hm! We all love you, and
will support no matter what.

339
00:19:27,393 --> 00:19:30,363
Please trust in me.

340
00:19:30,396 --> 00:19:34,901
Thanks a lot, Sailor Moon!...

341
00:19:36,069 --> 00:19:37,904
Sorry about yesterday.

342
00:19:37,971 --> 00:19:40,406
[chuckle]

343
00:19:41,074 --> 00:19:43,076
Well, Pao‐Pao Girl? What
are you waiting for?!

344
00:19:43,143 --> 00:19:47,047
Oh. Right. Paaoohhh!

345
00:19:47,080 --> 00:19:51,752
Please, Pegasus! Protect
everyone's dream!

346
00:19:54,821 --> 00:19:57,858
Twinkle Yell!

347
00:20:02,302 --> 00:20:03,970
[neigh]

348
00:20:17,450 --> 00:20:24,390
Moon Gorgeous Meditation!

349
00:20:35,468 --> 00:20:41,575
Stage Out!

350
00:20:45,078 --> 00:20:47,347
You'll pay for this!

351
00:20:50,350 --> 00:20:52,719
<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Pegasus... you came...</i>

352
00:20:52,753 --> 00:20:58,158
As long as you believe in
dreams... I will always
be by your side.

353
00:20:59,593 --> 00:21:03,436
<i>Thank you, Pegasus!</i>

354
00:21:05,105 --> 00:21:07,340
<i>(Hiroki)</i>
<i>Well. Here we go...</i>

355
00:21:07,373 --> 00:21:09,275
Don't worry, I've
got your back!...

356
00:21:09,275 --> 00:21:11,177
[panting]

357
00:21:11,211 --> 00:21:12,746
Keep it up!

358
00:21:12,779 --> 00:21:13,780
You've got it!

359
00:21:13,847 --> 00:21:17,784
I'm feeling good about
this, Kyusuke!

360
00:21:17,784 --> 00:21:20,020
Yeah! It'll fly this time!

361
00:21:30,731 --> 00:21:34,601
[gasps]

362
00:21:34,635 --> 00:21:36,603
They've done it!

363
00:21:36,637 --> 00:21:39,540
[happy laughter]

364
00:21:42,242 --> 00:21:43,977
Wow!

365
00:21:44,044 --> 00:21:46,780
<i>If you believe it,</i>
<i>you can do anything!</i>

366
00:21:46,813 --> 00:21:53,119
As long as you believe in
dreams, and in yourself, I will
always be by your side.

367
00:21:53,153 --> 00:21:57,558
<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Yes, I have faith in</i>
<i>you, Pegasus...</i>

368
00:21:57,591 --> 00:22:03,003
<i>I get it now... I've seen what</i>
<i>you can do when you believe in</i>
<i>something.</i>

369
00:22:03,003 --> 00:22:06,006
<i>You can make miracles happen!</i>

